Description: Naruto must battle an army of the undead controlled by Kabuto, who may also be controlling Itachi.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 58
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she explores her world through her new camera.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 11
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 7
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Himari is a cat-spirit sworn to protect teenage Yuto. This companion volume includes a design gallery and character guides.
Title: OMAMORI HIMARI, VOL. 0
Author: Milan Matra

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," the Cheshire Cat, disguised as a human named Boris, vies for Alice's affections.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: CHESHIRE CAT WALTZ, VOL. 2
Author: QuinRose

Description: Rika can see possible futures, but will she be able to alter the outcomes to save her and her friends from death?
Title: HIGURASHI WHEN THEY CRY, MASSACRE ARC, VOL. 1
Author: Ryukishi07

Description: The latest prosecution cases for Miles: a jewelry robbery with a dead thief and an art heist. Will justice be served?
Title: MILES EDGEWORTH, ACE ATTORNEY INVESTIGATIONS, VOL. 2
Author: Kenji Kuroda

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards.
Title: FAIRY TAIL 21
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.”
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 64
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Amityville High has a student body comprised of supernatural creatures, including Jack Frost.
Title: JACK FROST, VOL. 6
Author: JinHo Ko
